```kt
public void detectDevice(View v){
   // What is the orientation?
   Display display = 
   getWindowManager().getDefaultDisplay();
   txtOrientation.setText("" + display.getRotation());
   // What is the resolution?
   Point xy = new Point();
   display.getSize(xy);
   txtResolution.setText("x = " + xy.x + " y = " + xy.y);
}
```

